      "role": "user",
      "content": "it didnt feel like my brain was just linking things together though. it felt like the mug was actually... pulling the image of the bridge into my head. like a static charge. i know what you said about science but it felt way too specific to be a coincidence. if it was just an overactive brain why did it feel so physical? like i could literally taste the metallic smell of the bridge before it even happened?",
