      "content": "i just don't think it's a medical issue. doctors always try to pathologize things they don't understand. it feels more like a sense that is just... waking up. like i'm finally tuned into a frequency that was always there. if i'm not 'losing it,' then what if there's actually a reason why certain objects trigger these visions? like they're anchors to what's coming next?",
