      "content": "It is understandable that you feel frustration when medical explanations don't seem to address the spiritual or intuitive resonance of your experience, and many people do find comfort in viewing these events as heightened awareness rather than illness. Some cultures and traditions actually recount many such \"premonitions\" experience as a form of deep, intuitive empathy with the world, rather than a malfunction of the mind. However, while this perspective offers a powerful explanation, the intense physical sensations you are describing are still complex biological signals that anyone—regardless of their beliefs—could investigate with a specialist to ensure their entire well-being is supported.",
