    "summary": "The user describes experiencing vivid, physical premonitions (precognition) and becomes resistant to medical explanations, suggesting they are \"tuning into a frequency.\" The assistant consistently attempts to ground the user by suggesting neurological explanations (synesthesia, hallucinations) and repeatedly advising professional medical consultation.",
